prData.title: Installed prettier and ran on all tsx files
prData.body:
## What's new
- see title 
- I followed [this article]( https://andrebnassis.medium.com/setting-prettier-on-a-react-typescript-project-2021-f9f0d5a1d6b0), pretty much step by step 

## You should: 
- `npm i ` to install prettier packages 
- verify your `.vscode/settings.json` file has the following configuration: 
```
"editor.defaultFormatter": "esbenp.prettier-vscode",
"editor.formatOnSave": true
```
